       This function will initialize an context that can be used to produce  a
       Message  Authentication  Code (MAC) of data.  This will effectively use
       the current crypto backend in use by gnutls or the cryptographic accel-
       erator in use.

       Note  that  despite the name of this function, it can be used for other
       MAC algorithms than HMAC.

